{"tid":2064807,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"前線染疫消防始停用 K.Kwong：未達醫用級  救護國產口罩渣過CSi","createTime":"2020-06-15T05:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T06:06:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1f61c373123c15aeed74c6638c0b7f8193734842","tid":2064807,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:22:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200615/XCCR3K4HZCD5B2XXBCE6Q7I7BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200615%2FXCCR3K4HZCD5B2XXBCE6Q7I7BA%2F&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8hqcspSF5fyAY0%2FEGx5AO9c%3D&h=1a0cbb12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200615%2FXCCR3K4HZCD5B2XXBCE6Q7I7BA%2F&h=5c716e73\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200615/XCCR3K4HZCD5B2XXBCE6Q7I7BA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n前線染疫消防始停用 K.Kwong：未達醫用級 <br />\n救護國產口罩渣過CSi<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本月初一名救護員處理武漢肺炎確診患者後被傳染，事後消防處被揭發轉用劣質內地口罩始呼籲人員停用。本報日前從消防處內部獲得該款內地製「ECOLADY口罩」並委託「口罩專家」鄺士山（K.Kwong）測試，發現其保護能力只容市民探訪醫院使用，認為絕未達到醫護的保護級別。<br />\n<br />\n記者：鄧溢禧 廖承志<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6Z6XOCP7ELFMDHOSWYCOTLCWBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6Z6XOCP7ELFMDHOSWYCOTLCWBU.jpg&h=fad04e23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nK.Kwong指口罩予人感覺山寨，似「100蚊人仔樓下貨色」。李錦鏵攝<br />\n<br />\n現職消防處前線人員向本報透露，處方被傳媒揭發棄用懲教署CSi口罩，轉用劣質內地品牌ECOLADY後，已即時下令各救護站將該批口罩下架，但對傳媒則只說是「呼籲停用」。他認為單憑目測，已能分辨ECOLADY質素比CSi差，「更薄更透、剪開又有污點」，前線雖已向管理方反映問題，但感對方根本無意回應，亦未承擔監察裝備保護能力的基本責任。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：許樹昌：未有空氣播毒證據<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JVIM2JATEWLN4ONA65ZSKCJCNI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJVIM2JATEWLN4ONA65ZSKCJCNI.jpg&h=fbf7b5dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nECOLADY口罩被指比CSi更薄更透。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WHEU3TVGKLUWVDJGR6HVPKV6MQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWHEU3TVGKLUWVDJGR6HVPKV6MQ.jpg&h=ffce4f87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n口罩耳帶拉扯數次即斷裂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「100蚊人仔樓下貨色」<br />\n<br />\n中大化學系前講師鄺士山受本報委託，以耳帶構造、透氣度、防水能力與布料質素，測。。。。。。。。。。。。。外、到訪醫院無問題，但未達醫護級別，比懲教署的CSi口罩差。<br />\n<br />\n從拆盒開始，鄺士山已認為此款口罩予人「山寨」感覺，並不專。。。。。。。。。。。。。戴三、四次自動斷咗，如果喺街（斷）都唔係太驚，但你喺醫院點算呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n濾率未達國際最低標準<br />\n<br />\n至於透氣度和防水能力，鄺試戴樣本後再噴水實測，認為兩方面均合格，表層成功阻水，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。的最低保護級別「ASTM 等級1」，相信保護力比CSi還差，即連阻隔小量飛濺液體的保護力也不夠。<br />\n<br />\n感染及傳染病專科醫生曾祈殷指，世衞及醫管局要求人員為懷疑個案急救時，必須佩戴N95口罩、。。。。。。。。。。。。。口罩疑具質量問題，當局仍待商討跟進。部門已更換不同品牌且符合國際標準的外科口罩，經諮詢部門醫療總監後已分發前線使用。"},{"pid":"432e7ea02818c04380e86853915dcf65db0be33c","tid":2064807,"uid":214173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:25:09.000Z","msg":"公務員用散貨級口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36036ced082d24e873ba4aa90c890ba13b600e41","tid":2064807,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:26:25.000Z","msg":"香港要幫手清咁啲歐洲退貨"},{"pid":"08cf4f1c36cea894935022c611dd52e4211d8c9f","tid":2064807,"uid":78971,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"432e7ea02818c04380e86853915dcf65db0be33c","tid":2064807,"uid":214173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:25:09.000Z","msg":"公務員用散貨級口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:27:44.000Z","msg":"仲係最高危嘅救護員<br />\n跟得中國多，香港真係愈嚟愈離奇"},{"pid":"0b4e41a9186a51b7970ebe3f4e87ec42b5f53989","tid":2064807,"uid":112314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:35:38.000Z","msg":"希望用過哩款劣罩出勤嘅救護去check下...."},{"pid":"78f654